Package com.Software.FitnessSystem.AdminPageNavigation

Class NavigationControllerForAdmin

java.lang.Object
com.Software.FitnessSystem.AdminPageNavigation.NavigationControllerForAdmin
public class NavigationControllerForAdmin extends Object
Handles navigation for the admin pages in the fitness system. This class is responsible for controlling the flow between different admin pages by displaying the current page and executing the corresponding action based on the user's choice. It uses the Page class to manage individual page displays and actions.
Author:
Muath Hassoun

    • navigateTo

      public void navigateTo(Page page, AdminPagesController controller)
      Navigates to a specific page and allows the admin to interact with the page. Continuously prompts the user to enter a choice and executes the selected option. This method runs in an infinite loop, allowing the admin to interact with the page until they exit the program.
      Parameters:
      page - The page to navigate to.
      controller - The controller responsible for managing admin page actions.
